songs.title: Untitled Snippet (Day n Night Fest)*
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Christo
As we stand together in solidarity
Volatile villains we violate voluntarily
[?] or dare me, no stereo, too aware, too prepared
Suby, yeah, uhh

[Verse]
I'm a motherfuckin' NASA scientist with the pen
Half Leviathan strength, half giant
Intense criminal intent, big gentleman, big genitals
Big pendulum swing, [?] tip of the ring
Sharp tongue spark gun fight, niggas is slain
Blood trickles [?] in pain, dang
A little pencil [?] such a pivotal thing
Mix it with liquor and some chemical strains
[?] never pardon that individual
Sin him or kill him, give me the max or the minimum
Pull the trigger, kill as many millenials
In a minute, take the ball from the pen, tossed it, lost in the wind
Off with your favorite rapper head, we'll start with the limbs...
